query: SELECT rc.id, rc.userId, rc.vehicleId, rc.rentalStartDate, rc.rentalEndDate, rc.clientFirstName, v.brand, v.model, v.plateNumber FROM rentalContracts rc LEFT JOIN vehicles v ON rc.vehicleId = v.id WHERE rc.rentalStartDate >= '2026-02-20' ORDER BY rc.createdAt DESC LIMIT 1;
